Product name: BSDDP Hand Guard for Motorcycle Universal Hand Guard Protector for all Bikes – Metallic Green
Description:
BSDDP Hand Guard Green 
BSDDP Hand Guard Green shield the rider’s hands from wind, rain, cold weather, and flying debris, preventing injuries in case of a fall or collision. Riders can easily mount hand guards on the motorcycle handlebars, adjusting their position for optimal protection and comfort.
These hand guards feature aerodynamic designs, reducing wind resistance and minimizing buffeting at high speeds, enhancing motorcycle stability. Quality hand guards resist weather elements, keeping riders’ hands dry and warm. Some models include built-in wind deflectors for added protection. Certain hand guards incorporate reflective elements or bright colors, improving rider visibility in low-light conditions and enhancing overall safety. 
Well-designed hand guards allow seamless manipulation of controls like clutch and brake levers while providing essential protection, ensuring rider safety. Hand guards are designed for straightforward installation, requiring basic tools. They fit securely on the handlebars, eliminating wobbling or vibrations during riding. Manufacturers ensure hand guards are compatible with various motorcycle models, but it’s essential to confirm compatibility before purchasing. Hand guards are available in diverse styles and colors, allowing riders to choose designs that complement their motorcycle’s aesthetics. 
BSDDP Hand Guard Green feature additional functionalities, such as integrated LED turn signals, heated grips, or built-in wind deflectors, enhancing overall motorcycle utility.
 
Specification:
Material:PP Plastic And Aluminum Alloy
Size:15cm/5.91inch x 12.5cm/4.92inch x 5cm/1.97inch
Package Included:
2 x Motorcycle Handlebar Handguards Left + Right
